    region select-products (
        name: Select Products
        type: interactiveReport
        source {
            location: localDatabase
            type: sqlQuery
            sqlQuery:
                ```sql
                select
                    apex_item.checkbox2(
                    p_idx        => 1,
                    p_value      => id,
                    p_item_id    => 'P68_PRODUCT_IDS',    
                    p_item_label => 'Select/Unselect' || product_name) as product_id,
                    product_name,
                    product_family_id
                from
                    eba_cust_products
                order by product_name
                ```
